      *================================================================*
      *    Main                                                        *
      *================================================================*
       Main Section.
       main-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Open                                            *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        p-sub                =    "OO"
                     perform opn-out-000  thru opn-out-999
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Close                                           *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           else if   p-sub                =    "CO"
                     perform cls-out-000  thru cls-out-999
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Write Page                                      *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           else if   p-sub                =    "WP"
                     perform wrt-pag-000  thru wrt-pag-999
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Eject                                           *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           else if   p-sub                =    "EJ"
                     perform ejc-pag-000  thru ejc-pag-999
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Spool-Open                                      *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
