      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       opn-fil-pss-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Normalizzazione error-code                      *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      e-not-err            to   e-sts                  .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
