      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "A0"                 to   o-ope                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mopsys"
                                         using o                      .
      *
           move      "A5"                 to   o-ope                  .
           move      "fpx"                to   o-com                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mopsys"
                                         using o                      .
      *
           move      "A5"                 to   o-ope                  .
           move      "pss"                to   o-com                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mopsys"
                                         using o                      .
      *
           move      "A9"                 to   o-ope                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mopsys"
                                         using o                      .
      *
           move      o-pat                to   f-pss-pat              .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Operazione di Open                              *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           open      i-o    pss                                       .
       opn-fil-pss-999.
